title: My 10 Books - January 2014 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 diverse books in PDF and ePUB formats:

01. Alien Seas - Oceans in Space by Michael Carroll, Rosaly Lopes
02. American Politics Today - Essentials (3rd Ed) by William T. Bianco, David T. Canon
03. How to Study as a Mathematics Major by Lara Alcock
04. Human Communication in Society (3rd Ed) by Jess K. Alberts, Thomas K. Nakayamam, Judith N. Martin
05. Just Enough Spanish Grammar Illustrated by Gabriele Stobbe
06. Medicinal Chemistry - The Modern Drug Discovery Process by Erland Stevens
07. 101 Super-Easy Slow-Cooker Recipes by Gooseberry Patch
08. Essential Car Care for Women by Jamie Little, Danielle McCormick
09. The Can't Cook Book - Recipes for the Absolutely Terrified! by Jessica Seinfeld
10. The Dirty Side of Glamour by Tyler Shields
